row.InputSentence1: Holly asked her brother to put suntan lotion on her back.
row.InputSentence2: He took his time and applied it very carefully.
row.InputSentence3: Later that day, Holly wondered why people were laughing.
row.InputSentence4: She later realized her brother had made a design with the lotion.
row.RandomFifthSentenceQuiz1: Holly yelled at her brother to get back at him.
row.RandomFifthSentenceQuiz2: Holly gave her brother money as compensation.
